    <p></p>
    Hello and welcome to my about page! My name is <b>Adam Abad</b> and I currently go to <i>Wilkes University</i> where I am pursuing a major in Computer Science with a minor in Mathematics. I am a graduate of <i>Holy Redeemer Highschool</i>. I have a large interest in game design and game theory. Along with college, I work part time as a delivery driver at La Napolis in Mountain Top, PA. I also have several hobbies including Gunpla (Gundam plastic model kits) and collecting figures.
